<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>A platform in a shaft,
especially one of those between the series of ladders in a
shaft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sollar</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sollar
